Step 1: Set VS Code settings.json
Press Ctrl+Shift+P → Open User Settings (JSON) → add:
json"http.proxy": "http://a10-ep_proxy-ply-vip.uhc.com:8080",
"http.proxyStrictSSL": false
Step 2: Set System Environment Variables
Run CMD as Administrator:
cmdsetx HTTP_PROXY "http://a10-ep_proxy-ply-vip.uhc.com:8080" /M
setx HTTPS_PROXY "http://a10-ep_proxy-ply-vip.uhc.com:8080" /M
setx NODE_TLS_REJECT_UNAUTHORIZED "0" /M
Step 3: Import proxy into WinHTTP
Still in Admin CMD:
cmdnetsh winhttp set proxy a10-ep_proxy-ply-vip.uhc.com:8080
Step 4: Restart VS Code completely
Close all VS Code windows, then reopen.
